terraform init  -> installs the required pluggins from the terraform registry.
terraform plan  -> drafts the plan what is going to create.
terraform apply -> creates the resources at the target. 
terraform show   ->  shows the details of resources that were created.
terraform destroy -> destroys the resources which are created with that main.tf file.
terraform -var-file variables.tfvars  -> when we don't follow naming convention while calling the variables file while applying 
